      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Sensitivity of hemolysis predictions to all uncertain input parameters (fluid viscosity, hematocrit, power-law coefficients) must be documented with ranked importance measures.",
      "rationale": "Input sensitivity analysis was not completed. Monte Carlo sampling was initiated but results were not post-processed to produce ranked sensitivity indices; flagged as epistemic gap."
    },
    {
