      "factorType": "Test samples",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Sufficient experimental replicates must be available to characterize experimental variability at each validation operating point; minimum n=5 per condition at MRL 5.",
      "rationale": "Only n=2 replicates were available at each of the five operating points. Statistical characterization of experimental variability is insufficient to support MRL 5 validation uncertainty estimation; flagged as epistemic gap."
