    "rationale": "The credibility assessment for the VAD hemolysis CFD model has been reviewed. All 13 credibility factors have been evaluated against MRL 5 requirements. Seven factors were formally assessed; six remain as epistemic gaps. The assessment team concludes that the evidence package is complete and the model is accepted for regulatory submission based on the totality of evidence presented, including the Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification activities and the bench validation comparisons.",
